at the police academy.

3
00:00:18,280 --> 00:00:19,760
He's also the person I most admire

4
00:00:19,760 --> 00:00:20,800
in this world.

5
00:00:21,519 --> 00:00:22,800
He's smart, kind,

6
00:00:22,960 --> 00:00:23,879
righteous, and brave.

7
00:00:24,600 --> 00:00:26,280
Not only is he

8
00:00:26,400 --> 00:00:27,640
a great fighter and detective,

9
00:00:28,160 --> 00:00:30,519
but he's also good
at household chores and cooking.

10
00:00:30,960 --> 00:00:31,600
Zhibai,

11
00:00:32,399 --> 00:00:33,280
it smells great.

12
00:00:34,039 --> 00:00:34,799
Can I eat it now?

13
00:00:37,280 --> 00:00:39,000
Try it.

14
00:00:44,759 --> 00:00:45,479
Is it good?

15
00:00:46,920 --> 00:00:47,600
Yes.

16
00:00:50,119 --> 00:00:51,439
This rabbit is delicious.

17
00:00:51,620 --> 00:00:53,320
It was too skinny when it first arrived.

18
00:00:53,640 --> 00:00:55,280
Thankfully, you kept it so plump.

19
00:00:55,840 --> 00:00:57,840
If not, we wouldn't have enough
for two bites.

20
00:00:58,280 --> 00:00:58,880
What...

21
00:00:59,560 --> 00:01:00,600
What did you just say?

22
00:01:01,119 --> 00:01:01,719
The rabbit.

23
00:01:08,359 --> 00:01:10,040
Liao Zhibai, how dare you!

24
00:01:11,599 --> 00:01:12,680
Wait.

25
00:01:13,280 --> 00:01:14,000
Don't chase me.

26
00:01:14,359 --> 00:01:15,760
This is a chicken.

27
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:17,239
I was just kidding.

28
00:01:17,719 --> 00:01:18,840
Don't lie to me.

29
00:01:18,860 --> 00:01:20,690
- Is that how you see me?
- Where's my rabbit?

30
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:22,200
He always taught me

31
00:01:23,319 --> 00:01:25,799
that a man should have the courage
to conquer anything.

32
00:01:26,079 --> 00:01:26,760
Siyuan,

33
00:01:27,439 --> 00:01:28,120
go.

34
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:34,439
I gave you a Coke, so go now.

35
00:01:35,239 --> 00:01:35,920
Come on.

36
00:01:37,920 --> 00:01:38,560
Go on.

37
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:46,239
He also taught me

38
00:01:46,340 --> 00:01:47,350
to be forgiving, cheerful,

39
00:01:47,540 --> 00:01:48,920
and responsible for my own actions.

40
00:01:48,959 --> 00:01:51,159
Look at you. You dropped it again.

41
00:01:51,439 --> 00:01:52,920
What's wrong with you?

42
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:56,400
Rascal!

43
00:01:56,599 --> 00:01:57,280
Was it you?

44
00:01:57,359 --> 00:01:58,359
Not me.

45
00:01:58,439 --> 00:01:59,159
Not you?

46
00:01:59,280 --> 00:02:00,799
No, Mom.

47
00:02:01,239 --> 00:02:02,040
It was me.

48
00:02:03,519 --> 00:02:06,120
Please punish me. I broke the vase.

49
00:02:10,919 --> 00:02:12,960
It was you, little rascal!

50
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:15,680
Don't you run.

51
00:02:18,199 --> 00:02:19,159
Watch your steps.

52
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:21,719
Though we fight

53
00:02:22,719 --> 00:02:23,840
sometimes,

54
00:02:24,620 --> 00:02:25,960
Zhibai will always be the best

55
00:02:26,879 --> 00:02:28,199
in my heart.

56
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:30,759
I hope I can grow up quickly

57
00:02:31,159 --> 00:02:32,879
and become an amazing adult like him.

58
00:02:35,140 --> 00:02:37,520
So, what do you think of the essay?
Isn't it great?

