in similar cases before.

72
00:04:41,399 --> 00:04:42,920
I'd like to hear your opinion

73
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:46,279
on Liao Siyuan.

74
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:53,160
Well,

75
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:56,120
based on the available records,

76
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:57,360
on the day of the explosion,

77
00:04:57,439 --> 00:04:58,680
Liao Siyuan was indeed

78
00:04:58,680 --> 00:04:59,950
in a state of psychotic distress.

79
00:04:59,950 --> 00:05:02,320
He lost his ability to control himself
and recognize.

80
