Normally, patients can be exempt

81
00:05:04,100 --> 00:05:06,040
from legal responsibility
under traffic laws.

82
00:05:06,079 --> 00:05:08,240
Their family members and guardians

83
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:10,439
will handle the subsequent
civil compensation.

84
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:13,959
However, his condition is serious.

85
00:05:14,399 --> 00:05:15,879
He injured someone.

86
00:05:17,199 --> 00:05:18,319
One of his classmates and I

87
00:05:18,759 --> 00:05:20,000
were injured.

88
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:23,320
I won't pursue legal action against him.

89
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:25,360
As for the other victim,

90
00:05:25,519 --> 00:05:26,800
we've reached a settlement.

91
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:28,720
As his guardian,

92
00:05:29,199 --> 00:05:30,920
I'll oversee Siyuan's treatment

93
00:05:31,279 --> 00:05:33,199
in the following days.

94
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:35,959
Please be assured, sir.

95
00:05:41,199 --> 00:05:42,000
All right.

96
00:05:42,959 --> 00:05:44,720
Pay the fine and sign the paperwork.

97
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:47,759
Mr. Bian Ming, thank you so much.

98
00:05:47,879 --> 00:05:48,560
It's my duty.

99
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:50,800
Shu He, you stay.

100
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:51,800
The others are dismissed.

101
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:12,079
Many parties are involved
in this explosion.

102
00:06:12,080 --> 00:06:13,780
It has had tremendous influence.

103
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:16,439
Aside from the drug case in Buhe City,

104
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:17,480
several previous cases

105
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:19,160
have also resurfaced.

106
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:21,360
They are all connected

107
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:23,280
to the arson in Yong'an Village
ten years ago.

108
00:06:25,519 --> 00:06:27,399
Liao Siyuan is a key figure.

109
00:06:28,439 --> 00:06:29,439
He should be recused.

110
00:06:30,839 --> 00:06:31,879
Keep a close watch on him.

111
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:33,160
Yes, sir.

112
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:39,199
However, the top priority right now is

113
00:06:40,380 --> 00:06:42,560
that the first public exposure
of substantial AH7

114
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:45,480
has sparked discussion.

115
00:06:45,900 --> 00:06:47,390
The online discussion has run amok.

116
00:06:48,160 --> 00:06:50,600
The higher-ups are
very concerned about this case.

117
00:06:51,839 --> 00:06:54,319
We need to provide an answer
to the public as soon as possible.

118
00:06:58,160 --> 00:06:59,519
What's the progress?

119
00:07:01,460 --> 00:07:04,400
We've searched through
all the commercial premises in the city,

120
00:07:04,440 --> 00:07:05,780
but nothing has been found.

121
00:07:06,020 --> 00:07:08,800
The drug gift box is believed
to be offered only to fixed customers.

122
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:11,000
Judging by the crime scene,

123
00:07:11,100 --> 00:07:12,640
this is a large-scale production

124
00:07:12,640 --> 00:07:13,960
meant for long-term distribution.

125
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:15,480
We suspect

126
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:18,040
the mastermind behind Liu Haixun

127
00:07:18,460 --> 00:07:19,950
showed up at the scene that day.

128
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:21,959
We're verifying their identity.

129
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:25,519
Shu He.

130
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:31,279
This case is complicated.

131
00:07:31,280 --> 00:07:32,920
Issue a wanted notice immediately

132
00:07:33,060 --> 00:07:34,460
