133
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:43,439
All right, you may go.

134
00:07:59,879 --> 00:08:01,000
That's too small.

135
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:02,319
Officer Wang,

136
00:08:03,399 --> 00:08:04,759
