137
00:08:04,759 --> 00:08:06,519
He's caused a huge trouble.

138
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:08,720
He needs to be punished severely.

139
00:08:08,980 --> 00:08:10,920
If not, he wouldn't learn
from the lesson.

140
00:08:11,199 --> 00:08:13,199
The fine is a lot.

141
00:08:13,319 --> 00:08:14,279
It's not enough.

142
00:08:18,879 --> 00:08:20,399
Fortunately, no one died this time.

143
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:21,800
Otherwise,

144
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:24,040
