145
00:08:24,519 --> 00:08:25,319
Please count it.

146
00:08:25,399 --> 00:08:26,240
Yes, you're right.

147
00:08:29,879 --> 00:08:30,680
It's too much.

148
00:08:35,159 --> 00:08:35,960
Officer,

149
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:38,679
could you let me

150
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:40,159
check on my son?

151
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:43,320
There are rules.

152
00:08:43,519 --> 00:08:44,799
It's not up to us.

153
00:08:46,360 --> 00:08:47,159
Sign here.

154
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:50,799
Officer,

155
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:52,960
