156
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:54,919
I've been waiting all night.

157
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:00,799
Mom.

158
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:19,279
Go home.

159
00:10:03,371 --> 00:10:09,200
(Qi's Pharmacy, Healing hands
