160
00:10:09,279 --> 00:10:10,039
Come here.

161
00:10:16,679 --> 00:10:17,480
Stand still.

162
00:10:18,279 --> 00:10:19,799
Mom, not this again.

163
00:10:19,840 --> 00:10:21,720
I spent one night inside.
It's not necessary...

164
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:22,279
Step back.

165
00:10:28,679 --> 00:10:29,480
Again.

166
00:10:30,900 --> 00:10:32,360
First strike, to ward off calamity.

167
00:10:32,900 --> 00:10:34,540
Second strike, to beat tribulation.

168
00:10:35,559 --> 00:10:37,200
Third strike, to get rid of worries.

169
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:42,279
Take off your jacket.

170
00:10:56,480 --> 00:10:57,120
Jin.

171
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:09,919
Walk over it.

172
00:11:15,279 --> 00:11:16,559
Do I really have to?

173
00:11:16,879 --> 00:11:19,519
Walk through the flames.
Fire severs all bonds.

174
00:11:20,399 --> 00:11:21,840
All spirits or demons

175
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:23,720
shall vanish

176
00:11:25,039 --> 00:11:26,399
and haunt you no more.

177
00:11:27,679 --> 00:11:28,480
Walk through it.

178
00:11:31,240 --> 00:11:31,759
Do it.

179
00:11:35,535 --> 00:11:36,399
Come on.

180
00:11:40,420 --> 00:11:42,740
Do you refuse to let go
of the ghost pestering you,

181
00:11:42,759 --> 00:11:44,039
or is he holding you back?

182
00:11:49,600 --> 00:11:51,039
You're already dead.

183
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:53,799
Why won't you leave him alone?

184
00:11:54,519 --> 00:11:55,799
Why won't you leave

185
00:11:55,799 --> 00:11:56,679
our family alone?

186
00:11:56,759 --> 00:11:58,679
You're disturbing us.

187
00:11:58,799 --> 00:11:59,799
Go away!

188
00:11:59,879 --> 00:12:02,080
Just leave already!

189
00:12:02,919 --> 00:12:05,120
You claim to protect him,

190
00:12:05,279 --> 00:12:06,879
but what have you done?

191
00:12:07,080 --> 00:12:08,519
What have you really done?

192
00:12:09,039 --> 00:12:10,600
Hadn't you come back,

193
00:12:11,039 --> 00:12:12,759
