194
00:12:12,879 --> 00:12:14,320
Don't you care about him?

195
00:12:14,320 --> 00:12:16,559
He's lost a lot of blood.

196
00:12:17,480 --> 00:12:20,320
There are so many times
Siyuan almost...

197
00:12:21,039 --> 00:12:23,200
He almost died.

198
00:12:23,639 --> 00:12:25,480
He was so close to death.

199
