216
00:14:29,759 --> 00:14:32,960
Instead, it holds the runaway boy

217
00:14:34,480 --> 00:14:35,600
who couldn't face reality.

218
00:14:42,600 --> 00:14:44,279
I didn't mean to run away.

219
00:14:44,360 --> 00:14:45,159
I know.

220
00:14:47,360 --> 00:14:48,399
You were only ten.

221
00:14:49,279 --> 00:14:50,679
You couldn't do anything.

222
00:14:51,879 --> 00:14:53,200
That's why I wanted you to run.

223
00:14:53,639 --> 00:14:54,720
Run away from the fire.

224
