227
00:15:07,399 --> 00:15:09,039
like me, Dad, and Mom.

228
00:15:10,879 --> 00:15:12,840
I should've been with you all.

229
00:15:16,879 --> 00:15:18,320
I was such a coward.

230
00:15:21,759 --> 00:15:22,919
Even last night,

231
00:15:25,360 --> 00:15:27,279
