234
00:15:40,440 --> 00:15:41,559
Shu He was right.

235
00:15:43,679 --> 00:15:45,120
What I've been avoiding all along

236
00:15:47,279 --> 00:15:48,639
is my cowardice

237
00:15:50,720 --> 00:15:51,720
and insignificance.

238
00:15:53,919 --> 00:15:57,279
But every second, every minute
over the past ten years,

239
00:15:59,039 --> 00:16:00,320
you've been preparing yourself.

240
00:16:05,720 --> 00:16:06,519
Siyuan,

241
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:08,200
you've worked very hard.

242
00:16:09,240 --> 00:16:11,080
No one masters

243
00:16:11,200 --> 00:16:12,440
basic deduction in a day.

244
00:16:14,080 --> 00:16:16,200
No one picks up

245
00:16:16,200 --> 00:16:17,799
criminal profiling overnight.

246
00:16:18,639 --> 00:16:20,120
Through so many cases,

247
00:16:21,399 --> 00:16:24,159
you turned self-blame into courage

248
00:16:24,559 --> 00:16:27,080
and guilt into persistence.

249
00:16:28,519 --> 00:16:30,519
You've become an amazing adult.

250
00:16:36,320 --> 00:16:37,120
So

251
00:16:39,440 --> 00:16:41,240
you don't need my protection anymore.

252
00:16:49,159 --> 00:16:49,960
Can I?

253
00:16:54,720 --> 00:16:57,279
Face it or run from it,

254
00:16:58,360 --> 00:16:59,919
it's your choice.

255
00:17:00,120 --> 00:17:01,360
There's no right or wrong.

256
00:17:02,000 --> 00:17:03,360
If the present you

257
00:17:04,960 --> 00:17:07,480
still choose to leave,

258
00:17:08,680 --> 00:17:09,680
