259
00:17:10,839 --> 00:17:13,000
Let's pretend nothing has happened.

260
00:17:15,200 --> 00:17:17,000
You'll still be you,

261
00:17:18,640 --> 00:17:21,160
and I'll still be me.

262
00:17:23,160 --> 00:17:24,480
I'll always be with you.

263
00:17:28,839 --> 00:17:32,039
But Siyuan, it's been ten years.

264
00:17:34,559 --> 00:17:36,640
Are you sure you want
to make the same choice again?

